ART CITIES & VILLAGES” on 17th December 2016. Attended Second meeting of National Platform for Disaster Risk Reduction on “Disaster Risk Reduction for Sustainable Development: Making India Resilient by 2030” on 15 & 16 May 2017 at Vigyan Bhawan, Organised by Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India. Attended All India Workshop on “Extreme Loading on Structures” at India Institute of Technology on October 26-27, 2017. Participated in National Seminar on “Seismic Hazards and Mitigation of Structures” on 20 & 21 November 2017 at Jamia Millia Islamia, New Delhi. Attended one-week Short Term Course on “Advances Computing Tools in Civil Engineering (ACTCE 2018)”, conducted by Department of Civil Engineering, Indian Institute of Technology Kharagpur from 5-9 March 2018. Attended One Week Short Term Course on “Strengthening Capabilities for Hazardous and Disaster Risk Management (SCHDRM-2018)”, conducted by National Institute of Technology Kurukshetra, Haryana from May 1-6, 2018. Attended One Week Short Term Course on “Advances in Structural Engineering (AISE-2018)”, conducted by National Institute of Technology Kurukshetra, Haryana from May 14-19, 2018. Attended One day workshop on “Searching Drafting and Filling Process of the Patent”, organized by Intellectual Property Right Cell (IPRC) on September 29, 2018, at National Institute of Technology Kurukshetra. Attended One day workshop on “New Developments in Prefab Structures & Concrete Technology” organized by Department of Civil Engineering, National Institute of Technology Kurukshetra, Haryana on November 13, 2018. PUBLICATIONS/CONFERENCES 1. Rizwanullah, Sharma H.K. (2020) “Influence of Critical Parameters on UHPFRC Structural Elements Subjected to Blast Loading”, SN Applied Sciences, Vol. 2, No. 486, https://doi.org/10.1017/s42452-020-2259-5. (Scopus Indexed Journal) 2. Rizwanullah, Sharma H.K. (2022) “Blast Loading Effects on UHPFRC Structural Elements: A Review”, Innovative Infrastructure solutions, Vol. 7, No.