rete Congress Concrete: The Global Builder, organized by Dr B R Ambedkar National Institute of Technology Jalandhar, Punjab, India, March 5-8, 2019. 10. Rizwanullah, Mishra S., Sharma H.K., “Behaviour of UHPFRC under explosive loading: An Overview”, National Conference on Advances in Structural Technologies (CoAST-2019), organized by National Institute of Technology, Silchar, Feb 01-03, 2019. 11. Mishra S., Rizwanullah, Sharma H.K., Impact Analysis of Ultra-High-Performance Fibre Reinforced Concrete Slabs”, National Conference on Advances in Structural Technologies (CoAST-2019), organized by National Institute of Technology, Silchar, Feb 01-03, 2019. 12. Rizwanullah, Mishra S., Sharma H.K., “Behavior of UHPFRC under Explosive Loading: A Review”, International Conference on Sustainable Solutions in Industrial Pollution, Water and Wastewater Treatment, Organized by Department of Civil Engineering, Zakir Husain College of Engineering & Technology, Aligarh Muslim University, Aligarh in Collaboration with College of Engineering, The University of Toledo, USA, November 10-11, 2018. 13. Mishra S., Rizwanullah, Sharma H.K., “Analytical Modeling of NSC and UHPFRC Slab under Low Velocity Impact using ANSYS”, International Conference on Sustainable Solutions in Industrial Pollution, Water and Wastewater Treatment, Organized by Department of Civil Engineering, Zakir Husain College of Engineering & Technology, Aligarh Muslim University, Aligarh in Collaboration with College of Engineering, The University of Toledo, USA, November 10-11, 2018. 14. Mishra S. and Rizwanullah. “Comparative Analysis of Regular and Irregular Buildings with and without Shear Wall”, International Journal of Research and Scientific Innovation (IJRSI) | Volume IV, Issue VS, May 2017 | ISSN 2321–2705. Technical Skills: Auto Cad, STAAD Pro. ETAB, Primavera and MS Office. Languages Known: English, Hindi, and Urdu Extracurricular activities: Organizing member of Algorithm, CSI, Jamia Chapter by Civil Engineeri